Company Overview of Pemex Cogeneration and Services



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Pemex Cogeneration and Services generates, supplies, and sells electric and thermal energy and provides technical services and management associated with these activities. The company was founded in 2015 and is based in Mexico City, Mexico. Pemex Cogeneration and Services operates as a subsidiary of Petroleos Mexicanos.


